@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vlqsue(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.44 + v0 + 0.55) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.08)))
    v2 = (0.65 + (wp.sin(v0 + 0.27) + wp.exp(tmp + 0.64)))
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.sin(v0 + 0.53) - tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
